headline: POOL Q1 Earnings Call: Weather and Macro Conditions Pressure Results, Guidance Maintained
summary: Swimming pool distributor Pool (NASDAQ:POOL) fell short of the market’s revenue expectations in Q1 CY2025, with sales falling 4.4% year on year to $1.07 billion. Its GAAP profit of $1.42 per share was 4.1% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
